{"lemma":"كَشَفَةُ","slug":"كَشَفَةُ","root":"ك.ش.ف","root_slug":"ك-ش-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ش-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"كاشِف","root":"كشف","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n43040"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to divulge, to disclose, to reveal"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to discuss, to manifest, to demonstrate, to show"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reagent"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"radio detector"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"active participle of كَشَفَ (kašafa) from the root ك ش ف (k š f)."},"ipa":["/kaː.ʃa.fa/","/kaː.ʃif/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n43040","headword_ar":"كَشَفَهُ","root":"k$f","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uncovered it; unveiled it; laid it open; displayed it; exposed it to view; discovered it; detected it; revealed it; disclosed it."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$afa Eanohu","text_ar":"كَشَفَ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He investigated, explored,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scrutinized, it; searched, examined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inquired, into it."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$afahu","text_ar":"كَشَفَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a cover, or covering, or the like: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he uncovered it, laid it open,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$afa Eanohu","text_ar":"كَشَفَ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$afa $ayoA^F Eano $aYo'K","text_ar":"كَشَفَ شَيْاً عَنْ شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed, put off, took off, or stripped off, a thing from over,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from before, a thing which it covered or concealed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$afa","text_ar":"كَشَفَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed, cleared away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"grief, or sorrow: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraja","text_ar":"فَرَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(of which it is an explanation in the Msb and K). ―         -b6-  See 7."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}